&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="code-block-indented-with-four-spaces">Code block indented with four spaces&lt;/h3>
&lt;pre>&lt;code>&amp;lt;!doctype html&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;html lang=&amp;quot;en&amp;quot;&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;head&amp;gt;
